# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Eclipse Valhalla — Environment Variables
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your values.
# NEVER commit .env to git.
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ─── SUPABASE (Required for cloud mode) ──────────
# Get these from: https://supabase.com → Project Settings → API
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key-here

# ─── GEMINI AI (Required for Oracle / Forge) ─────
# Get from: https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
# NOTE: This key can also be set via Settings UI (stored in localStorage)
# VITE_GEMINI_API_KEY=your-gemini-key-here

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════
# NOTES:
#
# Without SUPABASE vars:
#   App runs in local-only/guest mode. All data in localStorage.
#
# Without GEMINI key:
#   Oracle/Forge features show "API key required" message.
#   Key can be entered in Settings → Gemini API Key.
#
# For Electron builds:
#   Same env vars. Vite injects them at build time.
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════
